{"id":63074,"title":"Quality and safety in pediatric hematology/oncology.","abstract":"Many principles of quality of care and patient safety are at the foundation of pediatric hematology/oncology. However, we still see too many errors, continue to have problems with communication, and the culture in many of our areas is still one of worrying about retribution when mentioning a problem. This review explores why specialists in pediatric hematology/oncology should be leaders in the field of quality and safety in healthcare.","date":"2014-04-16","categories":"Hemic and Lymphatic Diseases","split":"test","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24481936","annotations":[{"name":"Communication","weight":0.523185,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Communication"},{"name":"Health care","weight":0.149429,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health_care"},{"name":"Culture","weight":0.0370044,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Culture"},{"name":"Safety","weight":0.0206987,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Safety"},{"name":"Patient","weight":0.0180213,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patient"},{"name":"Error (baseball)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Error_(baseball)"},{"name":"Foundation (non-profit)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Foundation_(non-profit)"},{"name":"Field (agriculture)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Field_(agriculture)"},{"name":"Patient safety","weight":0.01593,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patient_safety"},{"name":"Retributive justice","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Retributive_justice"},{"name":"Quality (business)","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Quality_(business)"},{"name":"Pediatrics","weight":0.0113784,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pediatrics"}]}
